Package: plyrmr
Type: Package
Title: Data manipulation backed by rmr2 and Hadoop
Version: 0.1.0
Date: 2013-10-8
Author: Revolution Analytics
Maintainer: Revolution Analytics <rhadoop@revolutionanalytics.com>
